            "text": "In the video, we get video mounted to the front of a C8 Z06 as it speeds down a racetrack. That distinct flat-plane crank V8 sound is prominent, confirming that is the engine design, which we’ve heard repeatedly for a while. That’s great news, especially considering Ford iced the Voodoo when it ",
